    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将在“第一天”赦免 1 月 6 日的被告</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/trump-says-he-ll-aim-to-pardon-jan-6-defendants-on-first-day</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当选总统唐纳德·特朗普表示，他将在入主白宫“第一天”行使权力，赦免参与2021年1月6日袭击美国国会大厦的暴徒。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/trump-says-he-ll-aim-to-pardon-jan-6-defendants-on-first-day</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 14:39:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非民主联盟警告称，如果部长被解雇，政府将下台</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/south-africa-s-da-warns-of-government-exit-if-minister-is-fired</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非第二大政党的领导人表示，任何试图影响总统西里尔·拉马福萨解雇民主联盟下属“正在履行职责”的部长的企图都将“预示着”该国执政联盟的“终结”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/south-africa-s-da-warns-of-government-exit-if-minister-is-fired</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 14:12:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>工党计划“改革”规划系统以实现住房目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/uk-government-will-overhaul-planning-system-to-hit-house-targets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副首相安吉拉·雷纳在《每日电讯报》上撰文称，工党计划“彻底改革”规划系统，以实现其五年内在英国建造 150 万套新房的承诺。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/uk-government-will-overhaul-planning-system-to-hit-house-targets</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:51:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尹永哲逃脱弹劾 韩国将陷入更多动荡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/south-korea-set-for-more-turmoil-after-yoon-escapes-impeachment</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈上周末以微弱优势避免了弹劾。但要求他下台的压力却越来越大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-08/south-korea-set-for-more-turmoil-after-yoon-escapes-impeachment</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 08 Dec 2024 12:00:07 GMT</pubDate>
